Name: Eggs 1942
About the game: Take control of your egg and roll your way to victory! The Bad Eggs are mobilising their forces across the world. Join the Royal Egg Force and save the world with large scale eggy warfare. Eggs 1942 takes the singleplayer roll-a-ball concept, makes it egg shaped, places you in the centre of a large war with AI eggs and adds plenty of egg madness. Capture bases, crack a few eggs and keep on rolling your eggs.
